pistomp-recovery (0.1.0-7) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Updates picker now shows a "Checking for updates..." progress overlay
    while apt-get update runs in the background; auto-dismisses on completion.
  * Show a disabled "No internet" row in the System updates domain when the
    device has no network connectivity (TCP probe to 8.8.8.8:53).
  * Add "Update All" row to the System updates list when multiple packages
    have available updates.
  * Add browsepy, ffmpeg-pistomp, touchosc2midi, and lg to the tracked
    package list so they appear in update/rollback flows.
  * Sort Updates above Reset to Checkpoint and Factory Reset in the main menu.

 -- pistomp <pistomp@example.com>  Wed, 25 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

pistomp-recovery (0.1.0-6) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Start conflicting units (mod-ui, mod-ala-pi-stomp) with --no-block in
    start_main_app() so systemctl returns immediately; the previous blocking
    start deadlocked against our own Conflicts= (systemd had to stop recovery
    before the start could finish, but we were waiting on the start), which
    froze the LCD on Exit until systemd's stop timeout SIGKILLed us.

 -- pistomp <pistomp@example.com>  Tue, 23 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

